{"type": "article", "id": 4297, "title": "Instargram 实体相机", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-11T07:46:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060523330392vBnouGJ8N7SiC4.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t网络上传说了一年多的 Instargram 相机终于开启预售了。这款由 Instargram 与宝丽来联手推出的Socialmatic 实体相机已经吊足了粉丝的胃口，发布日期也从年中一直拖到了年末。它搭载了 1400 万像素主摄像头，200 万像素副摄像头，Android 系统，打印输出尺寸为 2＊3 英寸，使用宝丽来相纸，4.5 英寸触摸屏，4G 内存空间，支持 TF 卡扩展、蓝牙、WiFi、GPS。目前提供黑白两款可选，预售价 299.99 美元，<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Polaroid-Socialmatic-Digital-Instant-Camera/dp/B00QFVLL6U%3Fpsc%3D1%26SubscriptionId%3D07PVPGV9KPJSRT8N9GG2%26tag%3Ddealmoon-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB00QFVLL6U\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052333015t4eS3hDmXlTcbFY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233301PcEJmdgI0LW4SG9A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233302Yb6MBs7LujTfEi5n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233302it4xoke28vRGcaj5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233302AJcaVWdEelsGtqK3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233303KukTriUV3n0oJN7y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}